            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Emplibot is WordPress-only and tops out around 8 posts a month on the entry plan. RankYak runs flat-rate daily posts but no local or social. theStacc bundles 30 articles + Google Business Profile + social posting at $167/mo all-in, and publishes to WordPress, Webflow, and Ghost.</p></div></div>
